--- a/adtte_prog.R
+++ b/adtte_prog.R
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 1: Subgroup variable SUBGP is derived from SITEID using first 2 characters instead of SITEGR1 (pooled site group)
+Fix 1: SUBGP derived from SITEGR1 (pooled site group)
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 2: Stratified log-rank test uses unstratified survdiff() without strata() argument
+Fix 2: Log-rank uses strata() for stratified comparison
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 3: Median time-to-event calculation uses mean() instead of quantile(survfit, probs=0.5)
+Fix 3: Median uses quantile(survfit, probs=0.5)
@@ -1,5 +1,5 @@
-Bug 4: Treatment variable in survfit() uses numeric TRT01PN instead of factor, treating treatment as continuous
+Fix 4: Treatment variable converted to factor for categorical comparison

Summary of fixes:
1. SUBGP derived from SITEGR1 (pooled site group) (subgp_source)
2. Log-rank uses strata() for stratified comparison (logrank_strata)
3. Median uses quantile(survfit, probs=0.5) (median_calculation)
4. Treatment variable converted to factor for categorical comparison (trt_factor)
